{"tid":1683873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[批發]  軍火商降價！美國防部買F35獲調降12.7%","createTime":"2019-10-30T23:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T16:45:38.000Z","uid":141151,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e007c5c5beb2ee177289da5c6449f7abcbf7114c","tid":1683873,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:44:09.000Z","msg":"軍火商降價！美國防部買F35獲調降12.7%<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BB%8D%E7%81%AB%E5%95%86%E9%99%8D%E5%83%B9-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%E8%B2%B7f35%E7%8D%B2%E8%AA%BF%E9%99%8D12-7-012440464.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25BB%258D%25E7%2581%25AB%25E5%2595%2586%25E9%2599%258D%25E5%2583%25B9-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2598%25B2%25E9%2583%25A8%25E8%25B2%25B7f35%25E7%258D%25B2%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E9%2599%258D12-7-012440464.html&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHkn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=f56aa1f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BB%8D%E7%81%AB%E5%95%86%E9%99%8D%E5%83%B9-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%E8%B2%B7f35%E7%8D%B2%E8%AA%BF%E9%99%8D12-7-012440464.html</a><br />\n<br />\n物價不斷上漲，可是美國國防部購買軍機，卻從製造商取得1成多的折扣。美國國防部今天表示，已與洛克希德馬丁公司達成協議，採購F35的價格調降12.7%，這個價位將持續到2022年。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部官員表示，根據這份協議，美國政府花430億美元，能採購到478架F-35戰機。換算起來一架還不到1億美元。美國國防部指出，這次降價反應出製造商願意努力以更低的成本，打造出符合客戶要求，且性能擴增的戰機。洛克希德馬丁，將銷售目標瞄準已有F-16戰機的國家，希望以新的優惠價格，吸引老客戶下單。"},{"pid":"d5797696ba5627d4cec207c87e1e6244ffe2e965","tid":1683873,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:51:00.000Z","msg":"買多兩部打支那"},{"pid":"5c1e37cdf7b6232749edf1d866392b2ad6a513b7","tid":1683873,"uid":47392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:52:59.000Z","msg":"平賣幾部比台灣南韓日本啦"},{"pid":"915288f222d72803820d13f1cf613aa58d3a8bad","tid":1683873,"uid":24853,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:57:45.000Z","msg":"香港有錢 想買"},{"pid":"7d1cb4c9eb2d8d048c105d10b4